Litle bike hack tip: Buy bluetooth motorcycle TPMS sensors and get live tyre pressure on your mountainbike or fatbike ;) even when you use the handpump without pressure cauge.;)

If it's one of those cap sensor like fobo bike 2: buy thr T valve or drill another hole in the rim the valve just for the sensor, so you still can pump with the sensor mounted. One Extra benefit is that you can use the air station at the car station;)
